ConAgra Foods Offers to Acquire Ralcorp Holdings for $4.9 Billion in Cash

-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 
2011-05-04T10:01:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/conagra-foods-offers-to-acquire-ralcorp-holdings-for-4-9-billion-in-cash.html
ConAgra Foods Inc. (CAG)  said it has offered
to buy  Ralcorp Holdings Inc. (RAH)  for $86 a share in cash, or about
$4.9 billion, plus the assumption of $2.5 billion in debt.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  